 # Smart Task Analyzer[m
 [m
[31m-A intelligent task management system that scores and prioritizes tasks based on multiple factors including urgency, importance, effort, and dependencies.[m
[32m+[m[32mAn intelligent task prioritization system that helps users identify which tasks to work on first based on multiple factors.[m
 [m
 ## Features[m
 [m
[31m-- **Smart Priority Scoring**: Algorithm that considers multiple factors to calculate task priority[m
[31m-- **Multiple Sorting Strategies**: Choose between different prioritization approaches[m
[31m-- **Task Analysis**: Get detailed insights into why tasks are prioritized[m
[31m-- **Top Suggestions**: Receive personalized recommendations for what to work on next[m
[31m-- **Bulk Task Import**: Load tasks via JSON for quick setup[m
[31m-- **Responsive Design**: Works on desktop and mobile devices[m
[31m-- **Local Storage**: Your tasks are saved automatically[m
[31m-- **Django REST API**: Robust backend with full CRUD operations[m
[32m+[m[32m- Smart Priority Scoring: Algorithm considers urgency, importance, effort, and dependencies[m
[32m+[m[32m- Multiple Strategies: Choose between different prioritization approaches[m
[32m+[m[32m- Bulk Task Import: Load multiple tasks via JSON[m
[32m+[m[32m- Circular Dependency Detection: Automatically detects and warns about circular dependencies[m
[32m+[m[32m- Responsive Design: Works on desktop and mobile devices[m
[32m+[m[32m- Local Storage: Tasks persist between browser sessions[m
